Chris Rowe, 31, was diagnosed with an aggressive form of lung cancer .
He was sent home each time, reassured he was most likely suffering a virus .
But after noticing a dull ache in his ribs and coughing up blood, he was taken to A&E .
An X-ray revealed a tumour on the 31-year-old's lung .
The father-of-one has been told his cancer is inoperable .
His wife Kate is expecting their second child in June .